    return_speed = 0.8 * onward_speed + 0.1 * onward_speed
    return_time = distance / return_speed * 60 + repair_time
    total_time = onward_time + return_time
    total_speed = 2 * distance / (total_time / 60)
    return {'onward_speed': round(onward_speed, 2), 'return_speed': round(return_speed, 2), 'total_speed': round(total_speed, 2), 'onward_time': round(onward_time, 3), 'return_time': round(return_time, 2)}
